red you enough to fit yourself into YSJs high standards.\\r\\n\\r\\nIn your response, state your academic and mentoring goals, explaining how some aspects of YSJ would help you direct young researchers toward their potential.\\r\\n\\r\\nFurthermore, give examples of situations where you have helped learners wade through complex problems to aid their growth and excitement for science. \",\"third-essay\":\"Mentorship in scientific research requires a comprehensive understanding of the concepts and the ability to motivate and direct students as they go through their difficulties. Analyze this quote and discuss how your experiences and knowledge in scientific research have prepared you enough to fit yourself into YSJs high standards.\\r\\n\\r\\nIn your response, state your academic and mentoring goals, explaining how some aspects of YSJ would help you direct young researchers toward their potential.\\r\\n\\r\\nFurthermore, give examples of situations where you have helped learners wade through complex problems to aid their growth and excitement for science. Mentorship in scientific research requires a comprehensive understanding of the concepts and the ability to motivate and direct students as they go through their difficulties. Analyze this quote and discuss how your experiences and knowledge in scientific research have prepared you enough to fit yourself into YSJs high standards.\\r\\n\\r\\nIn your response, state your academic and mentoring goals, explaining how some aspects of YSJ would help you direct young researchers toward their potential.\\r\\n\\r\\nFurthermore, give examples of situations where you have helped learners wade through complex problems to aid their growth and excitement for science. Mentorship in scientific research requires a comprehensive understanding of the concepts and the ability to motivate and direct students as they go through their difficulties. Analyze this quote and discuss how your experiences and knowledge in scientific research have prepared you enough to fit yourself into YSJs high standards.\\r\\n\\r\\nIn your response, state your academic and mentoring goals, explaining how some aspects of YSJ would help you direct young researchers toward their potential.\\r\\n\\r\\nFurthermore, give examples of situations where you have helped learners wade through complex problems to aid their growth and excitement for science. \"}', '{\"research_files\":[{\"name\":\"BCI based games and Psychiatric disorders.pdf\",\"path\":\"uploads\\/SYSJ0170\\/drafts\\/BCI_based_games_and_Psychiatric_disorders.pdf\",\"size\":483010,\"type\":\"application\\/pdf\"}]}', '2025-07-03 05:31:09'),
('SYSJ0171', '{\"full-name\":\"Ghazal Elbasuny \",\"email-address\":\"zoo2aaadmissions@gmail.com\",\"contact-number\":\"*+201206580652\",\"country\":\"Egypt\",\"gender\":\"female\",\"birth-date\":\"2008-06-11\",\"institution\":\"Mohamed Metwally Elshaarawy school \",\"grade-year\":\"Grade 12\",\"gpa\":\"3.7\",\"interest\":[\"Aerospace Engineering,Computer Science,Data Science,Mathematics,Physics & Astrophysics\"],\"interest_ratings\":{\"Aerospace Engineering\":\"4\",\"Computer Science\":\"6\",\"Data Science\":\"5\",\"Mathematics\":\"9\",\"Physics & Astrophysics\":\"5\"},\"grade-previous\":\"I dont have these fields as subjects\",\"first-essay\":\"\",\"second-essay\":\"\",\"third-essay\":\"\",\"hours_commitment\":\"\",\"time_blocks\":\"\",\"hear_about\":\"\"}', '[]', '2025-07-03 23:25:38'),
