('SYSJ0387', '{\"full-name\":\"Salma Ahmed Ahmed\",\"email-address\":\"salmaahmedhamed94@gmail.com\",\"contact-number\":\"01091619198\",\"country\":\"Egypt\",\"birth-date\":\"2008-07-26\",\"institution\":\"Future Distinguished Official Language School 12   \",\"grade-year\":\"11\",\"gpa\":\"4.0 OUT OF 4.0\",\"interest\":[\"Biology\",\"Chemistry\",\"Computer Science\",\"Data Science\",\"Mathematics\",\"Medicine & Public Health\",\"Neuroscience & Neurobiology\",\"Physics & Astrophysics\",\"Psychology\",\"Robotics\",\"Sociology & Anthropology\"],\"grade-previous\":\"In Math and Science, I got  \",\"first-essay\":\"nn\",\"second-essay\":\"nn\",\"third-essay\":\"\",\"hours_commitment\":\"\",\"time_blocks\":\"\",\"hear_about\":\"\",\"gender\":\"female\",\"interest_ratings\":{\"Biology\":\"5\",\"Chemistry\":\"5\",\"Computer Science\":\"5\",\"Data Science\":\"5\",\"Mathematics\":\"5\",\"Medicine & Public Health\":\"5\",\"Neuroscience & Neurobiology\":\"5\",\"Physics & Astrophysics\":\"5\",\"Psychology\":\"5\",\"Robotics\":\"5\",\"Sociology & Anthropology\":\"5\"}}', '[]', '2025-07-04 20:35:17'),
('SYSJ0388', '{\"full-name\":\"Ahmed Ibrahim Sheded Kharboush\",\"email-address\":\"ahmedkharboush16@gmail.com\",\"contact-number\":\"01070260013\",\"country\":\"Egypt\",\"birth-date\":\"2008-03-03\",\"institution\":\"El-sadat STEM School\",\"grade-year\":\"12\",\"gpa\":\"3.7\\/4.0\",\"interest\":[\"Biology\",\"Chemistry\"],\"grade-previous\":\"A and A\",\"first-essay\":\"Scientific research mentoring requires a deep understanding of concepts, along with the ability to motivate and guide students through the challenges they face. Although I am still in high school, I believe these skills are not limited to age or grade level. Rather, they begin with a genuine passion for science and a desire to share knowledge with others.\\r\\nThroughout my studies, I worked hard to develop my understanding of scientific subjects through independent reading and participation in science activities both inside and outside of school. I often helped my peers simplify difficult topics in chemistry or physics by explaining them through diagrams or practical examples. These experiences taught me that the best way to understand any idea is to try to explain it to others. This has reinforced my desire to be part of a scientific environment that encourages collaboration and participation.\\r\\nMy academic goal is to become a researcher who can help solve real-life problems through science, and I aspire to participate in research teams working on issues of social concern. I also want to be a role model for other young students, sharing my experience and encouraging them to embark on research, even when the challenges are daunting.\\r\\nWhat distinguishes the Youth Science Program, in my opinion, is that it seeks not only academically outstanding students, but also curious minds, willing to learn, collaborate, and continually improve. I feel I possess these traits, and I look forward to being part of this inspiring scientific community.\",\"second-essay\":\"Hello Team 123,\\r\\nIhave noticed that you have not yet met your research proposal deadline, which is very important as it represents the foundation upon which we will proceed with the project. I know there are pressures or challenges that may delay the work, but we urgently need to see the proposal today so we can review and guide the team in a timely manner.\\r\\nPlease take an hour of your time today to finish at least the first draft. Its okay if its not completely complete, but the important thing is to start with a clear step. Remember, were here to learn, and repeated delays may affect the teams evaluation and continuity in the program.\\r\\nI look forward to your  before the end of the day. If you need any support or clarification, Im here to help.\\r\\nAll the best,\\r\\n[Ahmed Kharboush]\",\"third-essay\":\"My research background is based on a strong passion for biology and chemistry, which I have sought to develop through school projects, personal research initiatives, and participation in competitions and scientific activities inside and outside of school. Although I have not yet published research papers or obtained patents due to my current academic stage, I am always keen on scientific thinking and systematic experimentation.\\r\\nOne of my most notable experiments was a research project on the antibacterial effectiveness of natural plant extracts, such as garlic and clove oil, compared to commercial disinfectants. I designed the experiment, collected and analyzed the results, and then presented it at a school science fair, receiving praise from the judges for the clarity of the methodology and the accuracy of the analysis. This experience furthered my interest in microbiology and biochemistry.\\r\\nI also participated in group projects as part of the school science team, covering topics such as water purification, enzyme function, and the chemistry of everyday materials. I also enjoy attending scientific seminars and online courses in fields such as biotechnology and environmental chemistry, which have helped me expand my horizons beyond the school curriculum.\\r\\nI aspire to delve deeper into the intersection of biology and chemistry, particularly in the fields of drug development, environmental sustainability, and synthetic biology. I believe the Youth Science program is an ideal stepping stone to help me grow as a young researcher, connect with mentors, and contribute effectively to a distinguished scientific community.\",\"hours_commitment\":\"5\",\"time_blocks\":\" I spend several hours each week doing research, planning, and writing for a personal science project. I play sports or exercise almost every day to stay active and healthy. I take part in science and academic competitions, which need preparation and some full days during the summer.\",\"hear_about\":\"WhatsApp\",\"gender\":\"male\",\"interest_ratings\":{\"Biology\":\"5\",\"Chemistry\":\"5\"}}', '{\"research_files\":[],\"commented_files\":[],\"additional_files\":[{\"name\":\"ISEF_Poster_With_Comment_Metadata.pdf\",\"path\":\"uploads\\/SYSJ0388\\/drafts\\/686993242fbcf_ISEF_Poster_With_Comment_Metadata.pdf\",\"size\":913218,\"type\":\"application\\/pdf\"}]}', '2025-07-05 21:03:32'),
